  "name": "Bloodthirst Dagger",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<img src=\"Art%20-%20Items/weapons/dagger_evil_black_redeye_vampire.webp\" /><p>This cursed blade grows hungrier over time. In addition to its enchantment, the dagger now allows its wielder to cast <em>vampiric touch</em> twice per day, siphoning life from enemies to heal its owner. The weapon, originally crafted by a vampire assassin, was once used to betray allies during the Shining Crusade and has since passed through many hands. It radiates a sinister aura, feeding on the blood spilled by its wielder.</p>",
      "instructions": "",
      "unidentified": "<p>A kukri is a curved blade, about 1 foot in length.</p>"
    },
